OUTSIDE CONTAINER:
Start docker container: $ docker start ros_noetic
Access control list: $ xhost +local:root
Execute container: $ docker exec -it ros_noetic bash
Stop container properly: $ docker stop ros_noetic

IN CONTAINER:
Launch Gazebo Simulation: source ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash
			  source /opt/ros/noetic/setup.bash
			  LIBGL_ALWAYS_SOFTWARE=1 roslaunch franka_gazebo panda.launch
Load the Controller: rosservice call /controller_manager/load_controller   "name: 'cartesian_impedance_example_controller'"
Start the controller: rosservice call /controller_manager/switch_controller   "{start_controllers: ['cartesian_impedance_example_controller'], stop_controllers: [], strictness: 2}"
List active controllers: rosservice call /controller_manager/list_controllers
Command via terminal: rostopic pub -1 /cartesian_impedance_example_controller/equilibrium_pose geometry_msgs/PoseStamped "header:
  frame_id: 'panda_link0'
pose:
  position: {x: 0.3, y: 0.0, z: 0.5}
  orientation: {x: 0.0, y: 0.707, z: 0.0, w: 0.707}"
Stop the controller: rosservice call /controller_manager/switch_controller \
  "{start_controllers: [], stop_controllers: ['cartesian_impedance_example_controller'], strictness: 2}"


Build new scripts: catkin_make
		   source devel/setup.bash
		   
Build new python scripts and make them executable: chmod +x ~/catkin_ws/src/your_package/scripts/cartesian_impedance_publisher.py
Run the python script for control: source ~/catkin_ws/devel/setup.bash
				   rosrun my_franka_node  cartesian_impedance_publisher.py
				   
				   
Find for running: ps -ef | grep python
Kill them: 	  kill -9 #number
Kill all related to main: ps aux | grep main_BT.py | grep -v grep | awk '{print $2}' | xargs -r kill -9


LOAD BOTH CONTROLLERS: rosservice call /controller_manager/load_controller "name: 'position_joint_trajectory_controller'"
			rosservice call /controller_manager/load_controller   "name: 'cartesian_impedance_example_controller'"
			
Reconfigure gains: rosrun rqt_reconfigure rqt_reconfigure

